thread.title: Digital Catalyst

author: Digital Catalyst
title: Digital Catalyst
text:
As a micro business Digital Catalyst Group doesn't have the resources nor the need to maintain & manage an independent office.
The team at Servcorp, Market Street Sydney capably fulfils our office function, presents our business in fine style and provides us with the highest quality team support.
The staff are always pleasant & courteous, are always willing to assist in a timely fashion & leave us feeling confident that our daily office requirements & customer connections are being handled with competence & credibility.
We trust the Servcorp people & are proud to have them as a window to our successful web & software development business.
We highly recommend their service & facilities.
Michael Parsons
Director
